            "data": "How Constraints Are Automatically Applied"
        },
        {
            "type": "text",
            "data": "If the  Auto-Constraints  options are enabled in  System Preferences , the system automatically applies 2D constraints according to the methods you use to create new geometry. This topic identifies which constraints will be automatically applied for a variety of creation methods."
